pan><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/c48c31da297cecd0a2020225149a240e.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/c48c31da297cecd0a2020225149a240e.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/4faea913d3df626740cfba62c5dad876.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/4faea913d3df626740cfba62c5dad876.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/67fa0bce060cb1d5298169e9362e500f.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/67fa0bce060cb1d5298169e9362e500f.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/37d52d391fad06afd58a0ea4e042ccde.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/37d52d391fad06afd58a0ea4e042ccde.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/858c2670955d89a1b65ba6ea701a2ce5.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/858c2670955d89a1b65ba6ea701a2ce5.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/aa35142a75d6d3736741dcf00d8846db.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/aa35142a75d6d3736741dcf00d8846db.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/a5bd3194042427239e41f91edd2bb6cd.avif?t=1763677057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras_big/a5bd3194042427239e41f91edd2bb6cd.webp?t=1763677057 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ABOUT ENVIRA ENHANCE</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Envira Enhance is our advanced graphics system powered by DirectX, enabling Real-Time Global Illumination and enhanced shadows using Ray Tracing, as well as high-fidelity volumetric lighting.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality volumetric lighting generated with Quantum Volumetrics, part of the Envira Enhance ecosystem.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pulse Illumination is our ray tracing system that does not depend on RTX cores, and is composed of multiple functionalities such as Real-Time Global Illumination, which improves the behavior of lighting in the elements of the environment, as well as the reaction of objects, adding light bounces and transluminescence to certain materials and textures. Shadows also improve its behavior, such that it changes its rendering depending on its distance from a light source, this is possible thanks to our ShadingWorks system, which improves the shadows quality. <br>   </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For more information about advanced graphics quality and ray-tracing requirements, visit our website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Bakerville Case is a game created by one person. Please give your feedback and report any bugs to us, this will really help speed up development progress! Thank you very much.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/cfc61dca6f3522e9ff295f16342377ba.webp?t=1763677057\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140620/extras/4ad76cc3f81af8ab6f1a58acb4b37b5f.webp?t=1763677057\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p>",
